{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue la Ley}}}la Ley{\*\xmlclose} 1450 y 24 de {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue la Ley}}}
la Ley{\*\xmlclose} 1564 se ajustan a las condiciones establecidas en el art\'edculo 116 de {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\upr{\xmlattrvalue la Constituci?n Pol?tica}{\*\ud{\xmlattrvalue 
